Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0008,,{\blur3}宇宙:地球的灾难时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0008,,{\an8\blur3}太阳系后期重轰炸期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上溯至宇宙初始 周遭还只是一片漆黑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 忽地一声巨响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then... Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间空间以及物质皆由此发端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此后不断膨胀 延伸 永无止境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天 新的发现都在不断为我们解开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕴藏于这里的那些神秘莫测{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mysterious, the mind-blowing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人大开眼界 致命的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the deadly secrets of a place we call{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们称这个地方为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.28,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在其40多亿年的存在时间里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Throughout its more than 4 billion years of existence,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球经历了一些极其险恶的状况{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}planet Earth has endured some extremely rough days,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是最险恶的是什么呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but what were the very worst?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是和相距过近的行星发生碰撞吗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Was it a shadowing encounter with a planet that got too close?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管当时有什么 肯定也都灰飞烟灭了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Had anything been there, it definitely wouldn't have survived.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是炽热的致命射线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Or a hot shower of deadly rays{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎把地球上的生命扫荡一空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that almost scoured the planet clean of life?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后续的热浪涌向四面八方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The blast from the impact would have laid waves{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辐射范围达到数千公里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to thousand miles in every direction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以算得上是全球范围的声波{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's literally the sound waves around the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从摧毁一切的失控火山活动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}From runaway volcanism that led to vast extinctions{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到引发了全球深度冻结的微生物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to tiny microbes that triggered a global deep freeze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命在灭绝的边缘 摇摇欲坠{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Life is teetered perilously close to the break,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}time and time again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此次生物灭绝数量之多 可能空前绝后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}More life died then, than any time since and maybe any time before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是史上范围最广程度最惨烈的灭绝{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This was the biggest and the baddest of them all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最黑暗的时候已过去 还是潜伏在未来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are the darkest hours behind us or lurking in the distant future?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好准备 我们要倒数地球的七次灾难了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Take cover as we count down the seven worst days on planet Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许你认为你经历过一些困难的时刻{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You may think you've had some really rough days{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如严重的堵车{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}stuck in gridlock traffic,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上班途中人山人海{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}dodging the sea of humanity on their way to work{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遭遇一场暴雨或暴风雪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or trapped in a torrential down pour or blizzard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是这些情况跟地球的七次灾难相比{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But they can't even begin to compare{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全就是小巫见大巫{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to the seven worst days on planet Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纵观历史 地球遭遇过一些极其恶劣的情况{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Throughout its history earth has experienced some really bad days,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灭绝生命的 创造生命的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}days that have killed off life, created life,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及重塑整个地球的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}restructured the planet as a whole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有这些才形成了现今的地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All of this together has formed the Earth that we live on today,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是那些时期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but during those really bad days{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们绝对不想去经历{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we certainly wouldn't want to be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们看来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}From our point of view,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球确实经历过一些灾难时期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Earth has been through some pretty rough days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灾难性的冲击极大地改变了地貌{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Catastrophic impacts that have really changed the face of the planet{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改变了植物群和动物群{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and changed the makeup of the flora and fauna,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即地球上所有动植物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the animals and plants on the planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灾难时刻之一发生在地球的早期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One of Earth's worst days came early in its history{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一颗飞来横星猛冲而来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when an uninvited guest barged into our neighborhood{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在生命出现之际便将其扼杀在摇篮中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and threatened to destroy the planet before life had a chance to blossom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在我们就来探索地球第七大灾难时刻{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Let's dig in as the 7th worst day on Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忒伊亚星撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Theia impact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大约在45亿年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}About 4.5 billion years ago{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的太阳系是一片战场{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}our solar system was a battle zone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巨砾相互碰撞 融合 形成行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giant boulders collided and coalesced to form planets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早期的地球在灼烧形成之后不断遭到袭击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Infant Earth took hit after searing hit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我们有时光机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If we could somehow magically transport ourselves{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到早期的地球时期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}back in time to be in the time to be on the early Earth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为那会非常有意思{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it'd be very interesting, I think,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能够亲眼看看那些大事件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to watch one of these large impact events.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球表面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The surface of the Earth itself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炽热到接近熔点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}was probably heated to a nearly molten state.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大气层布满灰尘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The atmosphere would be very dusty,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分炎热{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you'd be very hot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是一个我们完全陌生的环境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So, it would be a very alien world to us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类不可能生存{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}one that we couldn't actually survive on{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能像现在这样站在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}just standing like we are here today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石块不断撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Pounding by incoming rocks,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球逐渐增至近似现在的体积{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Earth slowly grew to nearly its present size.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一个坚硬的地壳{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Developing a solid crust,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厚实的地幔{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a thick mantel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铁质地核{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}an iron core{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和炎热的大气层{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and a hot stormy atmosphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些人推测那时的生命非常脆弱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some speculate that life may have taken a tenuous hold{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但之后 就是灾难{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but then disaster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}邻近一颗叫忒伊亚的行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A neighboring planet named Theia{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}试图挤入地球的公转轨道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}had been edging into Earth's orbital path.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此次入侵以最具灾难性的形式结束{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The intrusion ended in the most disastrous way imaginable...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界大碰撞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A collision of worlds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是一次十分惨烈的事件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was a very violent event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象一下 火星质量的物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine something the mass of Mars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即地球质量的一成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}about 10% the mass of the Earth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从太空飞奔而来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}whacking in from space{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将自己撞得粉身碎骨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and blowing all its material.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时地球表面的所有物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Whatever was on the Earth at that time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都因这次事件面目全非{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it was radically changed by this event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当火星那么大的行星撞击地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When a Mars size object whacked in to the Earth,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可是地球的灾难日{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that was a bad day on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管当时有什么 肯定也都灰飞烟灭了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Had anything been there, it definitely wouldn't have survived.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整个灾难历时数小时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It took hours for the full scope of the catastrophe to unfold.{\r}
