Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球和忒伊亚星地幔的大部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and vast portions of both Earth's and Theia's mantels,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被抛射进入轨道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}were rejected into orbit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这跟电影里演的不一样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's not at all like what you see in the movies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可以坐下喝上一杯咖啡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You could sit down and have a cup of coffee{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发现还没撞完{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and it's still going on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大块物体撞击得花费很长时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These, like you know, big objects take a long time to incur,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}子弹打穿墙体那种火光可比不了这个{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so these aren't the normal flashes you'd think about bullets hitting a wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些喷射出的物质形成了一条巨大的轨道环{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The bloom of ejected material created a vast orbital ring{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后逐渐融合为地球的新伙伴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}before coalescing into a new companion for the Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是新生的月球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The new born, Moon.{\r}
