Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个碟状带的大部分物质撞击回地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This disc most of it came back and crashed back on to the Earth{\r}
