Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}融化的地壳逐渐冷却凝固{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and its molten crust to reharden.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管忒伊亚星撞击对地球来说是灾难{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But although the Theia impact was a very bad day on Earth,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但有助于地球形成适宜生命存在的条件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it was a very good day for its ability to sustain life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}月球形成后 地球的自转轴稳定了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When the Moon formed, it stabilized Earth's axis of rotation{\r}
