Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果这种影响没有产生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Would we even have life as we know it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球上能否有生命存在呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}if that impact had not taken place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果没有月亮 那么热带地区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Without a moon, you could really have a case with your tropics{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在经过几百万年后 可能会转过来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}within hundreds of thousands of years, could rotate{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}变成像两极地区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and become the Arctic or the Antarctic{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样所有生物就会死亡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and you kill everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当冲击结束后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}With the impact over,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}月球提供了轨道稳定性{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the Moon now providing orbital stability{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球的情况貌似安稳下来了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the stage seems set for a quiet future.{\r}
