Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行星形成 月球形成 皆大欢喜{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You formed the planets, you formed the Moon, everyone's happy{\r}
