Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给地球表面带来的贵金属{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}delivered precious metals to the surface of Earth.{\r}
