Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球上原先的这些贵金属{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Earth's original store these elements{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随着地球慢慢变冷 已沉入地心铁核{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}had sunken in its molten iron core as the planet slowly cooled.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是现在地球表面早已固化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But now with the planet already solidified,{\r}
